{% comment %}
============================================================
  PRODUCTOS DESTACADOS PRO — Carrusel de productos Shopify
============================================================
  Descripción:
  Sección de Shopify que muestra un carrusel horizontal de
  productos destacados, con scroll táctil, botones de
  navegación (prev/next) controlados por JavaScript, badges
  flotantes animados para los productos más vendidos, y
  generación de reseñas simuladas basadas en el ID del
  producto.

  Estructura del archivo (para referencia, en un tema real
  cada bloque va en su propio archivo):
    1. Section   -> sections/custom-product-showcase.liquid
    2. Snippet    -> snippets/custom-product-card.liquid
    3. CSS        -> assets/custom-product-showcase.css

  Tecnologías: Liquid, JavaScript (vanilla), CSS3, Shopify
  Schema (settings configurables desde el editor de temas).
============================================================
{% endcomment %}


{% comment %} ============================================
  1. SECTION FILE
     Archivo principal de la sección. Renderiza el título,
     el contenedor del carrusel y los productos de la
     colección seleccionada, usando el snippet de tarjeta
     de producto para cada uno.
============================================ {% endcomment %}

{{ 'custom-product-showcase.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<section class="custom-products">
  <div class="page-width">

    {% if section.settings.title != blank %}
      <h2 class="custom-products__title">
        {{ section.settings.title }}
      </h2>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="custom-carousel">

      <button class="carousel-btn prev" aria-label="Anterior">‹</button>
      <button class="carousel-btn next" aria-label="Siguiente">›</button>

      <div class="custom-products__grid">
        {% for product in section.settings.collection.products limit: section.settings.limit %}
          {% render 'custom-product-card', product: product, card_index: forloop.index %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

{% comment %}
  Lógica del carrusel: calcula el ancho de una tarjeta para
  desplazar el scroll exactamente ese ancho al hacer clic en
  los botones prev/next. El botón "prev" se oculta al inicio
  del scroll y reaparece automáticamente al desplazarse.
{% endcomment %}
<script>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {

  document.querySelectorAll('.custom-carousel').forEach(carousel => {

    const track = carousel.querySelector('.custom-products__grid');
    const btnNext = carousel.querySelector('.carousel-btn.next');
    const btnPrev = carousel.querySelector('.carousel-btn.prev');

    if (!track || !btnNext || !btnPrev) return;

    const card = track.querySelector('.custom-card');
    if (!card) return;

    const scrollAmount = card.offsetWidth + 14;

    // Ocultar botón izquierdo al inicio
    btnPrev.style.display = 'none';

    btnNext.addEventListener('click', () => {
      track.scrollBy({ left: scrollAmount, behavior: 'smooth' });
    });

    btnPrev.addEventListener('click', () => {
      track.scrollBy({ left: -scrollAmount, behavior: 'smooth' });
    });

    track.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
      if (track.scrollLeft > 20) {
        btnPrev.style.display = 'flex';
      } else {
        btnPrev.style.display = 'none';
      }
    });

  });

});
</script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Productos destacados PRO",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "title",
      "label": "Título",
      "default": "Nuestros favoritos"
    },
    {
      "type": "collection",
      "id": "collection",
      "label": "Colección de productos"
    },
    {
      "type": "range",
      "id": "limit",
      "label": "Cantidad de productos",
      "min": 2,
      "max": 12,
      "step": 1,
      "default": 4
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Productos destacados PRO"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}


{% comment %} ============================================
  2. SNIPPET FILE
     Tarjeta individual de producto, reutilizada dentro del
     for-loop de la sección mediante {% render %}. Recibe
     "product" y "card_index" como parámetros.
============================================ {% endcomment %}

{% comment %}
  snippets/custom-product-card.liquid
{% endcomment %}

<div class="custom-card">

  <div class="custom-image">

    {% comment %} Badge "Más vendidos" solo en los primeros 2 productos {% endcomment %}
    {% if card_index <= 2 %}
      <span class="floating-stock">
        Más vendidos
      </span>
    {% endif %}

    <img
      src="{{ product.featured_image | img_url: '600x600' }}"
      alt="{{ product.title | escape }}"
      loading="lazy"
    >

  </div>

  <div class="custom-info">

    {% comment %}
      Genera un número de "reseñas" pseudo-aleatorio pero
      consistente por producto, usando el ID real del
      producto como semilla (evita mostrar siempre el mismo
      número o requerir una app de reseñas externa).
    {% endcomment %}
    {% assign fake_reviews = product.id | modulo: 30 | plus: 20 %}

    <div class="custom-stars">
      ★★★★★ <span>({{ fake_reviews }})</span>
    </div>

    <h3 class="custom-title">
      {{ product.title }}
    </h3>

    <div class="custom-price">
      {% if product.compare_at_price > product.price %}
        <span class="old">{{ product.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
      {% endif %}
      <span class="new">{{ product.price | money }}</span>
    </div>

    <a href="{{ product.url }}" class="custom-btn">
      Lo quiero ❤️
    </a>

  </div>

</div>


{% comment %} ============================================
  3. CSS FILE
     assets/custom-product-showcase.css
     Estilos del carrusel: grid con scroll horizontal tipo
     "snap", tarjetas con efectos hover, badge animado, y
     versión responsive para mobile (2 columnas fijas).
============================================ {% endcomment %}

{% comment %}
<style>
/* --- Custom Product Showcase CSS --- */

@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');

.custom-products {
  padding: 10px 60px 60px;
  background: #0e0a0a;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

/* Orb de fondo */
.custom-products::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
  width: 800px;
  height: 400px;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(161,18,42,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}

.custom-products__title {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  text-align: center;
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: 5px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #c8913a;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.custom-carousel {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  padding: 20px 0;
}

.custom-products__grid {
  display: flex;
  gap: 14px;
  overflow-x: scroll;
  -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
  scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
  padding: 10px 5px;
  margin: -18px -18px;
  scrollbar-width: none;
  -ms-overflow-style: none;
}

.custom-products__grid::-webkit-scrollbar {
  display: none;
}

.custom-card {
  flex: 0 0 calc((100% - 42px) / 4);
  max-width: calc((100% - 42px) / 4);
  scroll-snap-align: start;
}

.custom-card {
  background: linear-gradient(145deg, #1a1010, #130c0c);
  border-radius: 18px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(200,145,58,0.2);
  box-shadow:
    0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.4),
    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(200,145,58,0.1);
  overflow: hidden;
  position: relative;
  transition: transform .3s ease, box-shadow .3s ease, border-color .3s ease;
}

.custom-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(200,145,58,0.5), transparent);
  opacity: 0.5;
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  z-index: 2;
}

.custom-card::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #A1122A, #c8913a, #A1122A, transparent);
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  z-index: 2;
}

.custom-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-7px) scale(1.015);
  border-color: rgba(200,145,58,0.45);
  box-shadow:
    0 20px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.55),
    0 0 0 1px rgba(200,145,58,0.2),
    0 0 25px rgba(200,145,58,0.12),
    0 0 40px rgba(200,145,58,0.07),
    0 0 20px rgba(161,18,42,0.1);
}

.custom-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
.custom-card:hover::after  { opacity: 1; }

.floating-stock {
  position: absolute;
  top: 10px;
  right: 10px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(95,14,28), rgb(161,18,42));
  color: #fff;
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 5px 10px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(250, 23, 15, 0.45);
  animation: floatPulse 2.6s ease-in-out infinite;
  z-index: 5;
}

@keyframes floatPulse {
  0%,100% { transform: translateY(0); }
  50%      { transform: translateY(-6px); }
}

.custom-image {
  padding: 10px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a1010, #130c0c);
}

.custom-image img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 250px;
  object-fit: contain;
  background: transparent;
  border-radius: 12px;
  transition: transform .3s ease, filter .3s ease;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.4));
}

.custom-card:hover .custom-image img {
  transform: scale(1.06);
  filter: drop-shadow(0 12px 24px rgba(161,18,42,0.3));
}

.custom-info { padding: 0px 10px 12px; }

.custom-stars {
  color: #c8913a;
  font-size: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 3px;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 4px rgba(200,145,58,0.4));
}

.custom-stars span {
  color: rgba(240,232,228,0.4);
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 300;
  margin-left: 4px;
}

.custom-title {
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: #f0e8e4;
  margin: 3px 0 7px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2px;
}

.custom-price {
  display: flex;
  gap: 7px;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.custom-price .old {
  color: rgba(240,232,228,0.3);
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 300;
  text-decoration: line-through;
}

.custom-price .new {
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #e8c97a;
  text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(200,145,58,0.4);
}

.custom-btn {
  display: block;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(95,14,28), rgb(161,18,42));
  color: #fff;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 9px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 1.2px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-decoration: none;
  border: 1px solid rgba(200,145,58,0.2);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(161,18,42,.3);
  transition: all .3s ease;
}

.custom-btn:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(161,18,42), rgb(200,26,26));
  border-color: rgba(200,145,58,0.45);
  box-shadow:
    0 8px 20px rgba(161,18,42,.4),
    0 0 14px rgba(200,145,58,0.12);
  letter-spacing: 1.6px;
}

.carousel-btn {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  width: 42px;
  height: 42px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(95,14,28), rgb(161,18,42));
  border: 1px solid rgba(200,145,58,0.3);
  color: #fff;
  font-size: 20px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  cursor: pointer;
  z-index: 50;
  box-shadow:
    0 6px 18px rgba(161,18,42,0.4),
    0 0 0 1px rgba(200,145,58,0.1);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.carousel-btn:hover {
  border-color: rgba(200,145,58,0.55);
  box-shadow:
    0 10px 25px rgba(161,18,42,0.5),
    0 0 15px rgba(200,145,58,0.15);
  transform: translateY(-53%);
}

.carousel-btn.prev { left: -22px; }
.carousel-btn.next { right: -22px; }

@media (max-width: 768px) {

  .custom-products {
    padding: 22px 10px 34px;
  }

  .custom-products__grid {
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    margin: -10px -8px;
  }

  .custom-card {
    flex: 0 0 calc((100% - 10px) / 2);
    max-width: calc((100% - 10px) / 2);
  }

  .custom-image img { height: 260px; }

  .custom-title { font-size: 11px; }

  .custom-price .new { font-size: 13px; }

  .custom-btn {
    padding: 6px;
    font-size: 10px;
  }

  .carousel-btn {
    width: 33px;
    height: 33px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .carousel-btn.prev { left: -9px; }
  .carousel-btn.next { right: -9px; }

  .custom-card:hover,
  .custom-card:hover::after,
  .custom-card:hover .custom-image img {
    transform: none;
    box-shadow: none;
  }

}
</style>
{% endcomment %}
